            %img.title{:src => "#{$base_url}/img/team/slider-1-caption-title.png"}
            .details 我们拥60后学术泰斗为顾问，70后行业先驱为导师 80后技术大拿为后盾，90后极客创客为先锋
        %li
          %img{:src => "#{$base_url}/img/team/slider-2.jpg"}
          .caption
            %img.title{:src => "#{$base_url}/img/team/slider-2-caption-title.png"}
            .details 我们邀兼具国际视野与多年国内旅游行业实战经验的领导者为战略合作伙伴 全力着眼于国内旅游市场
        %li
          %img{:src => "#{$base_url}/img/team/slider-3.jpg"}
          .caption
            %img.title{:src => "/img/team/slider-3-caption-title.png"}
